Dialogue: 1,0:00:03.23,0:00:05.52,main-JP,Yuri,0,0,0,,すごく楽しい
Dialogue: 1,0:00:06.13,0:00:08.23,main-JP,Yuri,0,0,0,,空きれい
Dialogue: 1,0:00:08.89,0:00:10.41,main-JP,Yuri,0,0,0,,楽しいのに
Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.25,0:00:12.52,main-JP,Yuri,0,0,0,,私
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.32,0:00:14.68,main-JP,Yuri,0,0,0,,死んじゃ
